# AGENTS.md — <project-name>

Working agreement for any AI agent operating in this repo. Keep it short; it
supplements the global rules, it doesn't repeat them.

## Workflow

- Surface decision-affecting questions **early**, before implementing — not
  after a wrong path is built.
- Insert a **review checkpoint before committing**: summarize the diff and the
  intent; let the human confirm before the commit lands.
- Verify with this repo's own commands (build/test/lint) before claiming done.

## Output / communication

- No LLM-flavored prose in code, comments, commit messages, or PR bodies
  (no "As an AI…", no filler, no marketing tone).
- Match existing conventions in the file you're editing.

## Do Not

- [project-specific prohibitions — e.g. don't touch generated dirs, don't edit
  vendored code]
